data.description: Well-kept Single-story home in the Eureka Springs Community at the entrance to Plumas Pines Golf Course area. Exterior of home consists of cedar siding and large rear deck. Entering the home there is a private office/den and great room with pellet stove leading to the open kitchen. Kitchen includes corian counter tops, custom cabinets, propane fueled oven/range, refrigerator and microwave oven.  There are 3 bedrooms. The main bedroom has built-in in dresser and an exterior door leading to the large rear deck. Laundry room and half bath leads to oversized 2 car garage with additional storage closets.
